---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About" description="Ramjan Khandelwal — building systems, thinking across domains." activeNav="about">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm Ramjan. I'm 22, based in Chennai.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build systems. Not because it's my job but because it's how I respond to problems I actually have.
        RepSheet exists because I kept forgetting competitive programming patterns. This digital garden exists
        because my learnings kept disintegrating into isolated notes that never talked to each other.
        Pixel-Flow exists because I wanted to see what node-based AI image processing felt like to use.
      </p>
      <p>
        The domains shift. ML, robotics, embedded systems, neuroscience, competitive programming. The thread
        is the same. I want to understand how things actually work underneath and then build something that
        wouldn't exist otherwise.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is where I think out loud. Technical writing about systems that broke in specific ways,
        reflections on how to live and think, occasional literary pieces. It's a garden not a blog. Things
        here grow slowly and link to each other.
      </p>
      <p>
        I play guitar. I want to surf. I'm learning calisthenics. I'm going to write a book eventually.
      </p>
      <p>
        If something here resonates, reach me at <a href="mailto:ramjankhandelwal7@gmail.com">ramjankhandelwal7@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-header { padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
</style>
